description: Hanging lanterns cast a gloomy light on the area, the dim illuminating highlight bits of metallic confetti littering the foliage of some shrubs growing to the east.  A few scraggly trees have had their spindly branches tied with streamers in an attempt to add an air of festiveness.

Sunlight highlights the colorful confetti littering the foliage of some shrubs growing to the east, particularly the small bits of metallic paper.  A few scraggly trees have had their spindly branches tied with streamers in an attempt to add an air of festiveness.
title: [Hang'em High]
